    <item>
      <title>国库在柔和的二月劳动力市场数据后延长了收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/treasuries-extend-gains-after-soft-february-labor-market-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在每月的就业报告显示出弱点的迹象之后，美国国债增加了，增加了2025年的收益，这使得交易者对今年晚些时候削减联邦储备金利率的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/treasuries-extend-gains-after-soft-february-labor-market-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗在2022年脂肪手指闪光崩溃上被瑞士交换调节器罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/citi-fined-by-swiss-exchange-regulator-over-2022-fat-finger-flash-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团（Citigroup Inc.）在伦敦员工的脂肪手指贸易造成了2022年欧洲股票的爆发事故后，被瑞士证券交易所监管机构罚款500,000瑞士法郎（568,000美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/citi-fined-by-swiss-exchange-regulator-over-2022-fat-finger-flash-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普贸易战争，制裁抓地力已经紧密的重油市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-trade-wars-sanctions-grip-already-tight-heavy-oil-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战争和制裁正在收紧繁重的原油市场，提高了石油的价格，并为美国最大的炼油中心筹集了成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-trade-wars-sanctions-grip-already-tight-heavy-oil-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国能源总监将寻求200亿美元以补充石油储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-energy-chief-plans-to-seek-20-billion-to-refill-oil-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国能源部长克里斯·赖特（Chris Wright）计划寻求高达200亿美元，以实现唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的目标，即将全国耗尽的石油储备金以最大能力加油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-energy-chief-plans-to-seek-20-billion-to-refill-oil-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯告诉吉尔特经济学家，她将限制英国的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/reeves-tells-gilt-economists-she-ll-restrain-government-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）周四会见了主要镀金经销商，在全球债券市场的激烈的比赛中，每年两次举行了两次新的会议，这导致了政府借贷成本的波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/reeves-tells-gilt-economists-she-ll-restrain-government-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 09:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
